'''Alphonse Menyo''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Gana]], azwi cyane muri filimi Freetow and Gold Coast Lounge

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i [[Accra]], muri [[Gana]]. Se, Bernard Menyo, yakomokaga muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba. Yahoze ari umunyeshuri w'ikigo cy'igihugu cya Filime na Televiziyo (NAFTI). Bernard yatsindiye igihembo mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou (FESPACO) kubera filime ''Whose fault'' . Nyina wa Menyo, Eugenia, yakomokaga muri [[Gana]] yakoraga mu muryango utegamiye kuri Leta. 

== Umwuga ==
Menyo yize muri Ghallywood Academy of Film Acting i Accra, muri [[Gana]] yiga sinema namakinamico. Yatangiye umwuga we wo gukina amakinamico mu 2009 akoresheje ikinamico. Muri 2015, yakinnye bwa mbere muri sinema muri filime yigenga y'Abanyamerika ''Freetown'' iyobowe na Garrett Batty.  Filime yerekanwe mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firimeÂ , kandi yatorewe ibihembo byinshi bya Gana Movie Awards . 

Menyo yerekanwe bwa mbere muri firime ''Utopia'' . Filime yakiriye ibihembo bine muri Ghana Movie Awards. Muri 2017, ''Utopia'' yabaye firime yonyine yo muri [[Gana]] yatowe kandi yerekanwa mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Helsinki (HAFF). Muri 2017, yakinnye muri triller y'urukundo rugufi ''Black Rose'' iyobowe na Pascal Aka . Muri 2018, yinjiye muri Pascal Aka ubutaha, akina muri firime ngufi ya ''Ruswa'' . Menyo yatsindiye igihembo cya Yaa Asantewaa mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Black Star kubera uruhare rwe ndetse anegukana igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza mu bagabo mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi ryabereye i [[Kinshasa]], muri [[Kongo]]. 

Yatoranijwe kugirango ahagararire [[Gana]] muri Theatre y'urubyiruko ya 2019 muri Egiputa. Nyuma yumwaka, yakinnye 'Daniel' muri film ya ''Gold Coast Lounge'' . Ku ruhare rwe, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza kurusha abandi muri Gana Movie Awards 2019. 

